us Plantarum (299V) 10 billion CFU","servingLabel":null,"supplementId":"1deaa8e5-58ec-56fc-ae06-41dc13d698ef"}]'::jsonb, '{"locale":"en","parser":"swisse_shopify_product_v1","titleEn":"Swisse Ultibiotic Daily Balance Probiotic","titleTh":"สวิส อัลติไบโอติก เดลี่ บาลานซ์ โปรไบโอติก","benefits":"Formulated based on scientific evidence to support general health and wellbeing with healthy bacteria (Probitic) 10 billion CFU. It''s suitable for active individuals and travellers on the go.","description":"Discover the benefits of Daily Balance Probiotics by Swisse. A trusted supplement for wellness and vitality in Thailand.","priceAmount":1760,"descriptionEn":"Swisse Ultibiotic Daily Balance Probiotic provides Lactobacillus Plantarum (299V) at 10 billion CFU per capsule to support general health and wellbeing.","descriptionTh":"สวิส อัลติไบโอติก เดลี่ บาลานซ์ โปรไบโอติก มีแลคโตบาซิลลัส แพลนทารัม (299V) 10 พันล้าน CFU ต่อแคปซูล เพื่อสนับสนุนสุขภาพและความเป็นอยู่ทั่วไป","extractedText":"Swisse Daily Balance Probiotics - Swisse Thailand Skip to content Products Back Products Beauty Eye Care Gummies Gut Health Immunity Joints, Bones, & Muscles Moisturisers Multivitamins Serums Skin Super Fruits & Herbs All Products Range Wellness Beauty Skincare About Back Our Story Ingredients Wellness Hub Sign in Search Cart (0) Cart empty Your cart is empty Continue shopping     svg]:w-full group-hover:text-uiGrey\"> Home / Daily Balance Probiotics   Skip to product information Open media 1 in modal Open media 2 in modal Open media 3 in modal Swisse Ultibiotic Daily Balance Probiotics Swisse Ultibiotic Daily Balance Probiotic has live-bacteria Lactobacillus Plantarum (299V) 10 billion CFU per capsule. It has been formulated based on scientific evidence to support general health and wellbeing, suitable for active individuals and travellers on the go. Swisse committed to contributing positively to the needs of society and the planet, and we are the carbon neutral company. #Probiotic #Lactobacillus #10billion Sale price 1,760 ฿ Where to buy Buy at TikTok Buy at Shopee Buy at Lazada Buy at Line Benefits Formulated based on scientific evidence to support general health and wellbeing with healthy bacteria (Probitic) 10 billion CFU. It''s suitable for active individuals and travellers on the go. Key Ingredients EACH CAPSULE CONTAINS: live-bacteria Lactobacillus Plantarum (299V) 10 billion CFU. Directions and Warnings DIRECTIONS : 1 capsule daily after dinner or before sleep and drink plenty of water afterwards. If diarrhoea persists for longer than 48 hours or symptoms such as nausea, vomiting, abdominal pain present, seek medical advice. ALLERGEN INFORMATION : No added lactose, gluten, yeast, egg, soy, artificial flavours or colours. Gluten free. Dairy free WARNINGS : Children and pregnant women should not consume. Do not use in weight control or reduction purposes. Should eat a variety of the five categories of food in appropriate proportions STORAGE : Store below 25C, in a cool, dry place. Do not use, if cap seal is broken. Reasons to love us We have been developing science-based formulas using premium ingredients sourced from around the world for over 50 years. We believe in natural ingredients being our hero ingredients. We also pursue the latest research findings to formulate our advanced product ranges and consistently strive to anticipate consumer demand. Backed by science Premium quality formula 50+ year heritage Certified B-Corp We are B-Corp Certified B Corps are for-profit companies that meet high standards of social and environmental performance, transparency, and accountability. Swisse is a brand of H&H Group, a certified B Corp. We feel honoured to be part of a global community using business as a force for good. Frequently Asked Questions What are probiotics, and what are their benefits? Probiotics are beneficial microorganisms, including bacteria and yeasts, that support overall health when consumed in appropriate amounts. They help regulate bodily functions, particularly in the digestive and immune systems, and may aid in preventing or managing certain health conditions. What are the benefits of the Lactobacillus probiotic strain? Lactobacillus is a type of beneficial bacteria naturally found in the digestive tract, urinary system, and reproductive organs. With over 50 known strains, some have been studied for their potential to alleviate or prevent digestive issues such as: Irritable Bowel Syndrome (IBS), Antibiotic-associated diarrhea, Clostridium difficile infection-related diarrhea, Traveler’s diarrhea, Lactose intolerance Beyond digestive health, Lactobacillus strains may also benefit conditions such as: Yeast infections, Bacterial vaginosis, Urinary tract infections, Respiratory infections, Skin conditions like cold sores, eczema, and mouth ulcers Is it safe to consume probiotic supplements? Probiotic supplements and probiotic-enriched foods are generally safe for most healthy individuals, with minimal risk of serious side effects. However, since long-term studies on probiotic use are still limited, and different strains may have varying effects, caution is advised. Individuals with pre-existing health conditions, weakened immune systems, recent surgeries, chronic illnesses, elderly individuals, young children, and pregnant women should consult a doctor before using probiotic products. Do we need to take vitamin supplements? The key is to ensure that we get a complete and balanced intake of nutrients each day. However, due to lifestyle limitations and dietary choices, we may not always receive the necessary nutrients in adequate amounts. In such cases, dietary supplements can be beneficial. Can Swisse products be taken alongside medication or medical treatments? Each individual has different nutritional and medicinal needs. If you are unsure whether Swisse products are suitable for you, it is best to consult a doctor. Please note that dietary supplements do not prevent, alter, or replace medical treatment or a well-balanced diet. What is the best time to take vitamins? Some supplements work best when taken with food, while others are more effective on an empty stomach. It is essential to follow the instructions on the label to maximize the benefits of each product. How long do dietary supplements last? In general, dietary supplements have a shelf life of approximately two years from the manufacturing date. Where does Swisse source its ingredients? We carefully select and source high-quality, premium-grade ingredients from around the world to ensure that only the best components go into our products. Where are Swisse products manufactured? Most of our products are manufactured in Australia. Please refer to the product packaging for the specific country of origin. The recommended dosage on the label applies to which age group? The recommended dosage is intended for individuals aged 18 and above. You may also like Swisse Ultibiotic Daily Active Probiotic Sale price 1,850 ฿ Swisse Lecithin Sale price 900 ฿ Our Products Beauty Eye Care Gut Health Gummies Immunity Joints, Bones, & Muscles Multivitamins Super Fruits & Herbs Skincare About Swisse Our Story Ingredients Help & Support FAQs Contact Us Privacy Policy Follow Us &copy; Swisse Thailand , 2026 Choosing a selection results in a full page refresh.\n\nBenefits Formulated based on scientific evidence to support general health and wellbeing with healthy bacteria (Probitic) 10 billion CFU. It''s suitable for active individuals and travellers on the go.\n\nKey Ingredients EACH CAPSULE CONTAINS: live-bacteria Lactobacillus Plantarum (299V) 10 billion CFU.\n\nDirections and Warnings DIRECTIONS : 1 capsule daily after dinner or before sleep and drink plenty of water afterwards. If diarrhoea persists for longer than 48 hours or symptoms such as nausea, vomiting, abdominal pain present, seek medical advice. ALLERGEN INFORMATION : No added lactose, gluten, yeast, egg, soy, artificial flavours or colours. Gluten free. 