ucts Shop All Products New Products Best Sellers Vegan Certified Women&#x27;s Health Men&#x27;s Health Kid&#x27;s Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition By Category Arthritis, Joint & Bone Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutritional Oils Heart Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition Kids&#x27; Health Men&#x27;s Health Multivitamins Muscle Support Nails, Hair & Skin Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health By Ingredient Calcium CoQ10 Curcumin Echinacea Fish Oil & Omega 3 Glucosamine Iron Magnesium Probiotics Selenium Vitamin B Vitamin C Vitamin D Vitamin E Zinc Health Hub By Categories By Type Latest Articles Action Plans Arthritis, Bone & Joint Beauty & Skincare Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutrition Oils Heart & Cardiovascular Health Kids & Infant Health Men&#x27;s Health Muscle Support & Fitness Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Recipes Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health Action Plans Articles Recipes Latest Articles About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Pillars Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Contact us Ask A Naturopath Our Newsroom Blackmores Subscribe Search Home Chevron Icon Horizontal products Chevron Icon Horizontal Blackmores Lutein Defence™ Size Size 60 tablets 120 tablets Good health changes everything - support your vision daily with Blackmores Lutein Defence™. This formula combines lutein and zeaxanthin, two important antioxidants that help reduce free radicals formed in the body and reduce free radical damage to body cells. It’s designed to support healthy eye function, including the macula and retina, and contributes to general health and wellbeing. Lutein and zeaxanthin are found in the eye and can be obtained from diets or supplements. Taken once daily, Blackmores Lutein Defence™ helps maintain the health of your eyes and vision with a focus on antioxidant protection. Product Format Tablet Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Read the warnings before purchase. Support For Eye Health Macula Health No Added Yeast No Added Gluten No Added Wheat No Added Dairy No Added Soya Bean Benefits & How To Use Benefits Supports eye macula health. Supports retina health. Contains antioxidants lutein and zeaxanthin to reduce free radicals in the body. Supports general health and wellbeing. Dosage Adults Take 1 tablet once a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions for use. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding, talk to your health professional before use. If symptoms persist talk to your health professional. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications, always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Benefits Dosage Warnings Supports eye macula health. Supports retina health. Contains antioxidants lutein and zeaxanthin to reduce free radicals in the body. Supports general health and wellbeing. Adults Take 1 tablet once a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food. Always read the label and follow the directions for use. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding, talk to your health professional before use. If symptoms persist talk to your health professional. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications, always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Ingredients Active ingredients per tablet: Lutein 10 mg Zeaxanthin 2 mg Lutein Defence™ Reviews Let&#x27;s stay in touch Instagram Facebook TikTok LinkedIn Back To Top About Blac