  ('e4ad7354-283d-42b6-a770-abf4240dc311'::uuid, 'f79618b3-4432-497c-8c41-76b31d9b03ae'::uuid, 'swisse', 'swisse', 'Magnesium', 'magnesium', 'Swisse Magnesium', 'สวิส แมกนีเซียม', 'https://swisse.co.th/products/magnesium', 'manufacturer_scrape', 'Stay energized and active with Magnesium by Swisse. Perfect for busy lifestyles in Thailand.', 'Swisse Magnesium supplement providing magnesium from citrate.', 'อาหารเสริมแมกนีเซียมจากสวิสในรูปแบบซิเตรต', array['http://swisse.co.th/cdn/shop/files/Swisse-Magnesium-1_85ea25a7-7586-42d2-8c3f-5d070eee7aa4.png?v=1757651430', 'https://swisse.co.th/cdn/shop/files/Swisse_Website_material_KV_refreshing_Jeff_1920x1280_c6a9be3f-27df-40f7-a318-9415721b23ef.jpg?v=1759210262&width=418%20418w', 'https://swisse.co.th/cdn/shop/files/Swisse-Magnesium-1_85ea25a7-7586-42d2-8c3f-5d070eee7aa4.png?format=webp&v=1757651430&width=124', 'https://swisse.co.th/cdn/shop/files/TH_19040-2_Swisse_Ultiboost_Magnesium_60_TABS_135_mL_3550x3550_RS.jpg?format=webp&v=1757651430&width=124', 'https://swisse.co.th/cdn/shop/files/TH_19040-2_Swisse_Ultiboost_Magnesium_60_TABS_135_mL_3550x3550_LS.jpg?format=webp&v=1757651430&width=124', 'https://swisse.co.th/cdn/shop/files/tik.png?crop=center&height=22&v=1743773592&width=22', 'https://swisse.co.th/cdn/shop/files/shopee.png?crop=center&height=22&v=1743773535&width=22', 'https://swisse.co.th/cdn/shop/files/Lazada.png?crop=center&height=22&v=1743773517&width=22']::text[], null, '[{"name":"Magnesium","unit":"mg","amount":150,"itemType":"supplement","sourceUrl":null,"confidence":"high","sourceText":"page_text: MAGNESIUM (from magnesium citrate 927.64 mg) 150 mg","servingLabel":null,"supplementId":"199df5c4-8921-5c37-b85b-6bcb14b443fa"}]'::jsonb, '{"locale":"en","parser":"swisse_shopify_product_v1","titleEn":"Swisse Magnesium","titleTh":"สวิส แมกนีเซียม","benefits":"Containing a bioavailable form of magnesium (citrate) for a physically active lifestyle. Factors such as insufficient dietary intake may affect magnesium levels in the body. - Magnesium is a component of bones and teeth. - Magnesium contributes to the normal function of the muscle and nervous system. - Magnesium contributes to normal energy-yielding metabolism","description":"Stay energized and active with Magnesium by Swisse. Perfect for busy lifestyles in Thailand.","priceAmount":600,"descriptionEn":"Swisse Magnesium supplement providing magnesium from citrate.","descriptionTh":"อาหารเสริมแมกนีเซียมจากสวิสในรูปแบบซิเตรต","extractedText":"Swisse Magnesium | Premium Wellness Supplements in Thailand - Swisse Thailand Skip to content Products Back Products Beauty Eye Care Gummies Gut Health Immunity Joints, Bones, & Muscles Moisturisers Multivitamins Serums Skin Super Fruits & Herbs All Products Range Wellness Beauty Skincare About Back Our Story Ingredients Wellness Hub Sign in Search Cart (0) Cart empty Your cart is empty Continue shopping     svg]:w-full group-hover:text-uiGrey\"> Home / Magnesium   Skip to product information Open media 1 in modal Open media 2 in modal Open media 3 in modal Swisse Magnesium SWISSE MAGNESIUM 150MG is a quality formula containing a bioavailable form of magnesium (citrate) for a physically active lifestyle. Factors such as insufficient dietary intake may affect magnesium levels in the body. Swisse committed to contributing positively to the needs of society and the planet, and we are the carbon neutral company. #Magnesium #Citrate Sale price 600 ฿ Where to buy Buy at TikTok Buy at Shopee Buy at Lazada Buy at Line Benefits Containing a bioavailable form of magnesium (citrate) for a physically active lifestyle. Factors such as insufficient dietary intake may affect magnesium levels in the body. - Magnesium is a component of bones and teeth. - Magnesium contributes to the normal function of the muscle and nervous system. - Magnesium contributes to normal energy-yielding metabolism Key Ingredients EACH TABLET CONTAINS: MAGNESIUM (from magnesium citrate 927.64 mg) 150 mg Directions and Warnings DIRECTIONS: 1 tablet daily. Take during or immediately after a meal, or as directed by a healthcare professional. WARNINGS: Children, and pregnant women should not consume. Should eat a variety of the five categories of food in appropriate proportions STORAGE: Store below 25C, in a cool, dry place. Do not use, if cap seal is broken. Reasons to love us We have been developing science-based formulas using premium ingredients sourced from around the world for over 50 years. We believe in natural ingredients being our hero ingredients. We also pursue the latest research findings to formulate our advanced product ranges and consistently strive to anticipate consumer demand. Backed by science Premium quality formula 50+ year heritage Certified B-Corp We are B-Corp Certified B Corps are for-profit companies that meet high standards of social and environmental performance, transparency, and accountability. Swisse is a brand of H&H Group, a certified B Corp. We feel honoured to be part of a global community using business as a force for good. Frequently Asked Questions What is the benefit of consuming Food high in magnesium daily? Factors such as insufficient dietary intake may affect magnesium levels in the body. Absorption: Formulated with a bioavailable form of magnesium (citrate) to help optimise absorption. Muscle Cramp Relief: Magnesium provides relief and helps reduce the occurrence of muscle cramps when dietary intake is inadequate. It also supports healthy muscle function and relaxation. Relieves Mild Muscle Spasms: Magnesium helps relieve and reduce mild muscle spasms and twitches when dietary intake is inadequate. Nervous System Support: Magnesium maintains a healthy nervous system and supports the body''s response to stress. Energy Production: Magnesium aids the metabolism of carbohydrates and fats to help convert them into energy. Heart Health Support: Magnesium supports heart health and maintains a healthy cardiovascular system. Do we need to take vitamin supplements? The key is to ensure that we get a complete and balanced intake of nutrients each day. However, due to lifestyle limitations and dietary choices, we may not always receive the necessary nutrients in adequate amounts. In such cases, dietary supplements can be beneficial. Can Swisse products be taken alongside medication or medical treatments? Each individual has different nutritional and medicinal needs. If you are unsure whether Swisse products are suitable for you, it is best to consult a doctor. Please note that dietary supplements do not prevent, alter, or replace medical treatment or a well-balanced diet. What is the best time to take vitamins? Some supplements work best when taken with food, while others are more effective on an empty stomach. It is essential to follow the instructions on the label to maximize the benefits of each product. How long do dietary supplements last? In general, dietary supplements have a shelf life of approximately two years from the manufacturing date. Where does Swisse source its ingredients? We carefully select and source high-quality, premium-grade ingredients from around the world to ensure that only the best components go into our products. Where are Swisse products manufactured? Most of our products are manufactured in Australia. Please refer to the product packaging for the specific country of origin. The recommended dosage on the label applies to which age group? The recommended dosage is intended for individuals aged 18 and above. You may also like Swisse Calcium + Vitamin D3 Sale price 550 ฿ Swisse Collagen MOV Sale price 1,350 ฿ Swisse Ultivite Multivitamin with B Vitamins Sale price 650 ฿ Swisse Ultivite Multivitamin with Folic Acid Sale price 650 ฿ Our Products Beauty Eye Care Gut Health Gummies Immunity Joints, Bones, & Muscles Multivitamins Super Fruits & Herbs Skincare About Swisse Our Story Ingredients Help & Support FAQs Contact Us Privacy Policy Follow Us &copy; Swisse Thailand , 2026 Choosing a selection