 1500 mg (Dietary supplement)","htmlLength":40413,"description":"Vitamin E and Selenium contributes to the protection of cells from oxidative stress.","descriptionEn":"Vitamin E and Selenium contributes to the protection of cells from oxidative stress.","descriptionTh":null,"extractedText":"Blackmores Bio C Acerola PLUS 1500 mg | Blackmores Club TH EN Member Sign Up Find Store Healthy Tips Products Favorite Pack World of Natural Health Natural Health Blackmores Institute About Blackmores Work with Us Ask the Expert --> News & Activities Blackmores Video News & Activities Blackmores Video Ask the Expert --> World of Natural Health Natural Health Blackmores Institute About Blackmores Work with Us Products Favorite Pack Healthy Tips Find Store  Log In Member Sign Up TH EN Health & Remedies      Health Hub       ALL Blackmores Bio C Acerola PLUS 1500 mg (Dietary supplement) About this product Rosehip extract and Acerola Cherry juice concentrate powder from natural raw material. Vitamin E and Selenium contributes to the protection of cells from oxidative stress. Vitamin C contributes to normal collagen formation for the normal function of skin. Features Blackmores Bio C Acerola PLUS 1500 mg Dietary Supplement Containing Acerola cherry juice concentrate powder 60 mg. form Acerola Cherry fruit fresh 1500 mg, Rosehip Extract, Grape Seed Extract, White Tea Extract, Concentrated Olive Fruit Powder plus Vitamin E, Zinc and selenium contributes to protection of cell from oxidative stress. Dosage Dosage: Adults – Take 1 tablet once a day with meal. Active ingredients Active ingredients per tablet: Rosehip Extract 100 mg (equivalent to Rosehip fruit dry 600 mg)   Acerola Cherry Juice Concentrate Powder 60 mg (equivalent to Acerola Cherry fruit fresh 1500 mg) Grape Seed Extract 50 mg (equivalent to grape seed dry 6000 mg)   White Tea Extract 25 mg (equivalent to white tea leaf dry 150 mg) Concentrated Olive Fruit Powder 10 mg   Vitamin E 10 mg (from D-alpha-Tocopheryl acid succina