tary intake is inadequate. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications, always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains approx. 64 mg of sodium per daily dose. Contains sulfites. Benefits Dosage Warnings Reduces symptoms of mild osteoarthritis. Added MSM to relieve mild joint pain and inflammation. Supports healthy joint cartilage growth. Supports joint mobility and flexibility. Reduces cartilage wear. Reduces mild joint swelling and stiffness. Supports general health and wellbeing. Adults Take 2 tablets two times a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food. KEEP OUT OF REACH OF CHILDREN. Always read the label and follow the directions for use. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding, or on warfarin therapy, talk to your health professional before use. If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional. Dietary supplements can only be of assistance if dietary intake is inadequate. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications, always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains approx. 64 mg of sodium per daily dose. Contains sulfites. Ingredients Active ingredients per tablet: Glucosamine sulfate sodium chloride 471 mg equivalent glucosamine sulfate 375 mg Bovine sodium chondroitin sulfate 200 mg Dimethylsulfane 375 mg equivalent MSM Ultra Relieve Joint Pain & Inflammation Reviews Let&#x27;s stay in touch Instagram Facebook TikTok LinkedIn Back To Top About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Approach Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Our Newsroom About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Approach Our People & Cultur