eves muscle cramps and reduces mild muscle spasms when dietary intake is inadequate.","descriptionEn":"Blackmores Magnesium supports muscle health, relieves muscle cramps and reduces mild muscle spasms when dietary intake is inadequate.","descriptionTh":null,"extractedText":"Blackmores Magnesium Tablets All Products Shop All Products New Products Best Sellers Vegan Certified Women&#x27;s Health Men&#x27;s Health Kid&#x27;s Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition By Category Arthritis, Joint & Bone Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutritional Oils Heart Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition Kids&#x27; Health Men&#x27;s Health Multivitamins Muscle Support Nails, Hair & Skin Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health By Ingredient Calcium CoQ10 Curcumin Echinacea Fish Oil & Omega 3 Glucosamine Iron Magnesium Probiotics Selenium Vitamin B Vitamin C Vitamin D Vitamin E Zinc Health Hub By Categories By Type Latest Articles Action Plans Arthritis, Bone & Joint Beauty & Skincare Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutrition Oils Heart & Cardiovascular Health Kids & Infant Health Men&#x27;s Health Muscle Support & Fitness Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Recipes Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health Action Plans Articles Recipes Latest Articles About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Pillars Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Contact us Ask A Naturopath Our Newsroom Blackmores Subscribe Search Home Chevron Icon Horizontal products Chevron Icon Horizontal Blackmores Magnesium Size Size 50 tablets 100 tablets 200 tablets Blackmores Magnesium is formulated with Magnesium Citrate, a well absorbed form of magnesium to increase magnesium levels in the body. It supports muscle health and relieves muscle cramps and mild muscle spasms and maintains cardiovascular system health when dietary intake is inadequate. It also supports nervous system function. Product Format Tablet Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Read the warnings before purchase. Support For Muscle Cramps Muscle Health Fatigue Nervous System Health Heart and Cardiovascular Health Energy No Added Yeast No Added Gluten No Added Wheat No Added Dairy Benefits & How To Use Benefits Improves magnesium levels in the body. Supports muscle health, muscle function and muscle relaxation. Relieves muscle cramps, mild muscle spasms and muscle twitches when dietary intake is inadequate. Supports cardiovascular system health when dietary intake is inadequate. Supports healthy sleeping patterns. Supports nervous system function and a healthy stress response in the body. Supports energy levels and body electrolyte balance. Supports bone health and healthy teeth. No added preservatives. No added artificial flavours, colours or sweeteners. Dosage Adults General Health - Take 1 tablet once a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Muscle Cramp & Mild Muscle Spasm Relief - Take 2 tablets once a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Do not exceed 2 tablets in 24 hours. Take with food. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions for use. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding, talk to your health professional before use. If symptoms persist talk to your health professional. Dietary supplements can only be assistance if dietary intake is inadequate. If you have any pre-existing conditions, or are on any medications, always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Benefits Dosage Warnings Improves magnesium levels in the body. Supports muscle health, muscle function and muscle relaxation. Relieves muscle cramps, mild muscle spasms and muscle twitches when dietary intake is inadequate. Supports cardiovascular system health when dietary intake is inadequate. Supports healthy sleeping patterns. Supports nervous system function and a healthy stress response in the body. Supports energy levels and body electrolyte balance. Supports bone health and healthy teeth. No added preservatives. No added artificial flavours, colours or sweeteners. Adults General Health - Take 1 tablet once a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Muscle Cramp & Mild Muscle Spasm Relief - Take 2 tablets once a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Do not exceed 2 tablets in 24 hours. Take with food. Always read the label and follow the directions for use. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding, talk to your health professional before use. If symptoms persist talk to your health professional. Dietary supplements can only be assistance if dietary intake is inadequate. If you have any pre-existing conditions, or are on any medications, always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. The Blackmores Difference Ingredients Active ingredients per tablet: Magnesium citrate 970.8 mg equivalent magnesium 150 mg Magnesium Reviews Let&#x27;s stay in touch Instagram Facebook TikTok LinkedIn Back To Top About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Approach Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Our Newsroom About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Approach Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Our Newsroom Our Brands & Products Shop Our Products Shop Best Sellers BioCeuticals Blackmores Professional Blackmores Institute Blackmores Education Our Brands & Products Shop Our Products Shop Best Sellers BioCeuticals Blackmores Professional Blackmores Institute Blackmores Education Inter