o general health and wellbeing. It aids in the production of healthy red blood cells and helps maintain vitamin B12 within the normal range—important for those whose dietary intake is not adequate. Whether you&#x27;re following a vegetarian diet or simply looking for daily nutritional support, this formula provides a source of vitamin B12. Good health changes everything—support your daily energy with Blackmores Vitamin B12. Product Format Tablet Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Read the warnings before purchase. Support For Energy No Added Wheat No Added Gluten No Added Yeast No Added Soya Bean No Added Dairy Vegan Certified Benefits & How To Use Benefits Supports energy levels. Assists healthy red blood cell production. Supports general health and wellbeing. Dosage Adults Take 1 tablet two times a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions for use. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding, talk to your health professional before use. Supplements may only be of assistance if dietary intake is inadequate. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Benefits Dosage Warnings Supports energy levels. Assists healthy red blood cell production. Supports general health and wellbeing. Adults Take 1 tablet two times a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food. Always read the label and follow the directions for use. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding, talk to your health professional before use. Supplements may only be of assistance if dietary intake is inadequate. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, ple