d at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains sulfites. Benefits Dosage Warnings Enhances magnesium levels in the body. Supports muscle health, muscle function and muscle relaxation. Relieves muscle cramps, mild muscle spasms and muscle twitches when dietary intake is inadequate. Supports cardiovascular system health when dietary intake is inadequate. Supports healthy sleeping patterns. Supports nervous system function and a healthy stress response in the body. Supports energy levels and body electrolyte balance. Supports bone health and healthy teeth. No added artificial flavours, colours or sweeteners. Adults General Health - Take 1 tablet once a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Muscle Cramp & Mild Muscle Spasm Relief - Take 2 tablets once a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Do not exceed 2 tablets in 24 hours. Take with food. Always read the label and follow the directions for use. If symptoms persist talk to your health professional. Dietary supplements can only be assistance if dietary intake is inadequate. If you have any pre-existing conditions, or are on any medications, always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains sulfites. The Blackmores Difference Ingredients Active ingredients per tablet: Magnesium glycinate 1.1 g equivalent magnesium 150 mg Magnesium Glycinate Reviews Let&#x27;s stay in touch Instagram Facebook TikTok LinkedIn Back To Top About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Approach Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Our Newsroom About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Approach Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Our Newsroom Our Brands & Products Shop Our Products Shop Best Sel