ins vitamin E which is an antioxidant and that helps maintain healthy cholesterol & blood lipids and supports blood vessel health.","descriptionEn":"Contains vitamin E which is an antioxidant and that helps maintain healthy cholesterol & blood lipids and supports blood vessel health.","descriptionTh":null,"extractedText":"Vitamin E 1000IU All Products Shop All Products New Products Best Sellers Vegan Certified Women&#x27;s Health Men&#x27;s Health Kid&#x27;s Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition By Category Arthritis, Joint & Bone Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutritional Oils Heart Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition Kids&#x27; Health Men&#x27;s Health Multivitamins Muscle Support Nails, Hair & Skin Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health By Ingredient Calcium CoQ10 Curcumin Echinacea Fish Oil & Omega 3 Glucosamine Iron Magnesium Probiotics Selenium Vitamin B Vitamin C Vitamin D Vitamin E Zinc Health Hub By Categories By Type Latest Articles Action Plans Arthritis, Bone & Joint Beauty & Skincare Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutrition Oils Heart & Cardiovascular Health Kids & Infant Health Men&#x27;s Health Muscle Support & Fitness Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Recipes Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health Action Plans Articles Recipes Latest Articles About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Pillars Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Contact us Ask A Naturopath Our Newsroom Blackmores Subscribe Search Home Chevron Icon Horizontal products Chevron Icon Horizontal Blackmores Vitamin E 1000 IU Size Size 30 capsules 100 capsules Blackmores Vitamin E 1000IU provides a high-strength dose of vitamin E in a convenient one-a-day capsule. Vitamin E is an antioxidant that helps reduce free radical damage to body cells. It also helps maintain healthy cholesterol and contributes to the maintenance of healthy blood lipids. In addition, vitamin E helps support blood vessel health and maintain general health and wellbeing. Taken daily, it supports vitamin E levels in the body and provides antioxidant protection. Good health changes everything—support your daily wellness with Blackmores Vitamin E 1000IU. Product Format Capsule Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Read the warnings before purchase. Support For Healthy Cholesterol Antioxidant for Free Radical Damage Halal Certified No Added Yeast No Added Gluten No Added Wheat No Added Dairy Benefits & How To Use Benefits Helps maintain healthy cholesterol & blood lipids. Supports blood vessel health. Is an antioxidant to help protect cells from free radical damage. Helps maintain vitamin E levels in the body. Maintains general health and wellbeing. High strength dose. Dosage Adults Take 1 capsule once a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Supplements may only be of assistance if dietary intake is inadequate. Do not use in children. Do not use during pregnancy or breastfeeding. Do not use if you have pre-existing severe heart disease (such as heart attack or stroke). If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications, always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains soya bean products and sulfites. Benefits Dosage Warnings Helps maintain healthy cholesterol & blood lipids. Supports blood vessel health. Is an antioxidant to help protect cells from free radical damage. Helps maintain vitamin E levels in the body. Maintains general health and wellbeing. High strength dose. Adults Take 1 capsule once a day, or as prescribed by a health profe